<!DOCTYPE HTML>

<html>
	<head>
		<title>SitWith Reservation Officer</title>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="layout/ReserveOfficerStyle.css" type="text/css"/>
		
	</head>
	<body>

			<section id="header" class="dark">
				<header>
					<div class="information">
						<div id="information_container">
							<div id="logo">
								<img src="layout/images/logo_big.png"/>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</header>
				<div class="title">
					<table>
						<tr>
							<td id="title_td">
								<div id="title_container">
									<h2>Reserve Officer Association</h2>
								</div>
							</td>
							<td id="backtohome_td">
								<div id="backtohome">
									<a href="index.jsp">Back to home page</a>
								</div>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</table>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<div id="content_container">
						<div id="introduction">
							<p>SitWith is a program that organizes lunches for groups of four at restaurants in the Pittsburgh area in order to help create interesting conversation and connections over a relaxed lunch</p>
							<p>SitWith lunches are easy - and we're organizing one specifically for the members of the Reserve Officer Association in the Pittsburgh area.  Just register and and let us know if you're free. 
							 We'll make a reservation and email you to confirm once we can make a table of four.</p>
						</div>
						<div id="form">
							<table>
								<tr>
									<td id="registration_td">
										<div id="registration">
											<p class="sign_title">Don't have an account? Sign up!</p>
			                                    <p class="subtitle">First Name</p>
			                                    <div class="field"><input type="text" id="fName" name="fName" placeholder="First Name"></div>
			                                    
												<p class="subtitle">Last Name</p>
			                                    <div class="field"><input type="text" id="lName" name="lName" placeholder="Last Name"></div>
												
			                                    <p class="subtitle">Email</p>
			                                    <div class="field"><input type="text" id="Email" name="Email" placeholder="Email Address"></div>
			                                            
			                                    <p class="subtitle">Password</p>
			                                    <div class="field"><input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password"></div>
			                                    
												<p class="subtitle">Confirm Password</p>
			                                    <div class="field"><input type="password" id="password2" name="password2" placeholder="Re-enter Password"></div>
												<br/>
												<input type="submit" class="signup_submit" name="signup_submit"/>
										</div>
									</td>
									<td id="sign_td">
										<div id="sign">
											<div id="sign_ROE">
												<p class="sign_title">Already have an account? <br>Please sign in and leave your information</p>
												<p class="subtitle">Preferred Area</p>
												<div class="field"><input type="text" id="ROE_area" name="ROE_area" placeholder="Area in Pittsburgh"></div>
												<p class="comment">Downtown, Southside, The Strip, Oakland, Shadyside . . . etc.</p>
												<input type="submit" id="sign_ROE_button" value="Sign up for January 21st - 12:30 pm"/>
											</div>
											<div id="sign_anothertime">
												<p class="sign_title">Not free January 21st?  Let us know a better time</p> 
												<input type="text" id="time" placeholder="Date and time"/><br/><br/>
												<input type="submit" id="sign_time" value="submit"/>
											</div>
										</div>
									</td>
								</tr>
							</table>
						</div>
					</div>
					
				</div>
				<div id="footer">
					<div id="footer_container">
						<ul class="icons">
							<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sitwithco" id="facebook_logo"><img src="images/fb.png"/></a></li>
							<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?screen_name=SitWithCo" class="twitter-mention-button" id="twitter_logo" data-size="large" data-related="SitWithCo"><img src="images/tw.png"/></a></li>
						</ul>
						<div class="copyright">
							<ul class="menu">
								<li>SitWith. All rights reserved.</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			

	</body>
</html>